install guide:
$ git clone -b develop https://github.com/syl20bnr/spacemacs ~/.emacs.d
$ git clone https://github.com/xuuexu/spacemacs.d ~/.spacemacs.d
$ emacs

however, installing some dependencies brings me lots of trouble, I do have plan to write a script to reslove some missing binary files.

- Haskell : ghcup -> cabal, stack, ghc (https://develop.spacemacs.org/layers/+lang/haskell/README.html#dependencies)
- Coq : brew -> coqtop
- Agda : cabal -> Agda (https://develop.spacemacs.org/layers/+lang/agda/README.html#agda)
- Racket : brew -> racket, raco -> drracket
